{"type": "article", "id": 30755, "title": "为镜子扮上狂野部落风｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-08-08T23:00:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 31258, "name": "Mu Design"}, {"id": 31259, "name": "Maya Pindeus"}, {"id": 31260, "name": "Johanna Pichlbauer"}, {"id": 31261, "name": "Teddy Moissant"}, {"id": 31262, "name": "Joel Beebe"}, {"id": 31263, "name": "Jumphol Socharoentham"}, {"id": 31264, "name": "Pakawat Vijaykadga"}, {"id": 31265, "name": "Mark Canavarro"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160808215430KYxybRU03MZoCqOl.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>A Play Of Dependencies by Maya Pindeus &amp; Johanna Pichlbauer</h3><p>你还记得那个用来鼓励同事之间进行交流的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/30542.html\">花盆系统</a>吗？这个需要两个人共同参与操作的灯具 A Play Of Dependencies 有着异曲同工之妙：灯具的两端含有磁性，由于中间的电力回路受到阻断，需要安装上木头与黄铜制成的连接器才能使电路接通。设计师 <a href=\"http://www.mayapindeus.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maya Pindeus</a> 和 Johanna Pichlbauer 希望通过这个需要动手组装的设计将人与人之间的互动带回职场。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215848qDthp0f8UmN3ZMS6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215848rBnFWHsGwxNAzlia.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215849Z17ATcBj62qYNhyb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215849uxMhP1RFyUfgWETr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215850dIN0eQ83TYnR96ow.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215850hTHwlvkrs7UuQqO1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Tribu marabout de ficelle by Teddy Moissant</h3><p>你有没有好奇过自己穿上部落风格的服饰会是什么样子？<a href=\"http://www.teddy-moissant.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Teddy Moissant</a> 以传统的部落服饰为灵感设计了一组名为 Tribu marabout de ficelle 的镜子，为家具环境注入了一股自由奔放的气息。镜子的外围巧妙地利用了软木塞和流苏模拟出头饰的细节，这样人们就可以在这些五颜六色的镜子前看到自己更具有“狂野精神”的一面，兼具了装饰性与实用性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608082159417CDPVxMIa406bNXE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.117359\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215942FGkQcxUoi1dmW8ue.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.528117\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215943Dgf2EYoPtwmsyZR7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215945wTKrd2elcCMVZy4W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.528117\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215944ts7yZVAIv80UGgeD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.528117\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215948nljQphyFAU3RL8gY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.528117\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Hula Wrap by Joel Beebe</h3><p>对 MacBook 用户来说，如何整齐地收纳充电器是一个不小的烦恼，由设计师 Joel Beebe 领导的团队为此特别设计了一款专用的收线器 Hula Wrap。这个由皮革制成的外套能够有效地保护 MagSafe，电源线可以缠绕在外并通过扣子固定，使用时只要打开扣子接上延长的 AC 电源线即可。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1031801104/hula-wrap-macbook-cable-organizer\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 25 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215754FL5yaWZjEwBHs2gi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215754jh8zrMW4ev0lqEVm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215755Pm5cY7GVeAvbEnh0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.435294\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215814PHuV0AxRrpm5wslL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.519118\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Bearbot by Mu Design</h3><p>家里的遥控器太多？这个由 <a href=\"http://mu-design.lu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mu Design</a> 设计的小熊“管家”可以让你轻松实现家庭自动化。有着黑熊外形的 Bearbot 其实是一款智能遥控器，与家电配对后你可以通过内置的 3D 手势控制器通过它进行各种操作。Bearbot 在激活时会时不时变化自己的表情与你互动，可以持续使用 4 个小时，不使用的话它就会进入最长可达一个月的“冬眠期”。由于 Bearbot 的有效距离为 5 米，Mu Design 还专门设计了一个迷你版 Bearbot 作为红外继电器。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/bearbot#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 75 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215601ZKI10QmBhug52pP7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215655467YbmjFxQRqyXGA.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642857\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608082157063p6ShRLvwBdPyHV2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608082157135pE6M3hmPvN0iog8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.762857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608082157241JNo0aK95rzSpDcZ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.474000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>ALATO Cabinet by Jumphol Socharoentham &amp; Pakawat Vijaykadga</h3><p>Jumphol Socharoentham 和 Pakawat Vijaykadga 都是在泰国先皇理工学院（KMITL）主修家具设计的学生，他们以羽翼为灵感设计了这个名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/41332845/ALATO-CABINET\" rel=\"nofollow\">ALATO</a> 的柜子。柜子由四根黑色金属管支撑，两扇木门上的木管穿插在表面被喷洒上渐变色的“羽毛”间，从两边打开的样子就像是鸟儿展开翅膀一样，富有新意。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215531SrvOzENUub4ojK3Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215531Qt5Es4yhRKrxflBd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016080821553353ocKlB2IupytFAb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215533NCAI04ZUBweQ8ucD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.677500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608082155342Qlp69nO30CPvkr1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.605833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Zero Gravity Rack by Mark Canavarro</h3><p>对于那些想在小空间里放上滑板甚至是一辆单车的人来说，这个名为 Zero Gravity Rack 的折叠型墙面储物架可以助你“一臂之力”：设计师 Mark Canavarro 利用空气压缩技术让这个架子最多可以支撑起 22 千克重的物品，有效地提升了空间的利用率。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/590223522/zero-gravity-racks-the-storage-rack-everyone-needs/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 119 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215507Q5XnazwdS1qpOPKx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.752941\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215507QwiAG0o2tPnkDjva.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.369118\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215507fWhRvwKqneS97VJg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215508PoK6RLNQ7Mf8ivVt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.486250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}